                "html": "<p>Betamethasone valerate 0.025% cream and ointment: moderate.</p><p>Betamethasone valerate 0.1% cream, lotion, medicated plasters, ointment, and scalp application: potent.</p><p>Betamethasone valerate 0.12% foam: potent.</p><p>Betamethasone dipropionate 0.05% cream, lotion, and ointment: potent.</p>"
